---------------
Gob Online Chat - ReadMe
---------------

Version: 0.4 (alpha)
Author: Ken Barber (ken@bob.sh)

1. Introduction

This is the Beta release of Gob.

Gob is a chat program that provides a Java chat server and chat client in the 
form of a Java Applet.

